# Deploy Conventions

## Docker Compose Services

| Service | Image | Port | Depends On |
|---------|-------|------|------------|
| mysql | mysql:8.0 | 3307 | — |
| openfga-migrate | alpine:3.19 | — | mysql |
| openfga | openfga/openfga:v1.5.3 | 8180, 8181, 3001 | mysql, openfga-migrate |
| openfga-init | alpine:3.19 | — | openfga |
| clickhouse | clickhouse-server:24.8 | 8123, 9000 | — |
| clickhouse-init | clickhouse-server:24.8 | — | clickhouse |
| otel-collector | otel-collector-contrib:0.137.0 | 4317, 4318, 8888, 13133 | clickhouse |
| vector | Build `../vector/` | 8686, 14317, 14318 | — |
| pulse-ui | Build `pulse-ui/` | 3000 | pulse-server |
| pulse-server | Build `backend/server/` | 8080 | mysql, clickhouse, openfga |
| pulse-alerts-cron | Build `backend/pulse-alerts-cron/` | 4000 | mysql, pulse-server, clickhouse |

**Note:** pulse-ai runs via its own `docker-compose.yml` in `pulse_ai/` (port 8000). Manage with `cd pulse_ai && ./setup.sh [start|stop|restart|logs|clean]`.

## Network

All services on `pulse-network` (bridge). Internal references use container names (e.g., `mysql`, `clickhouse:8123`, `openfga:8080`).

## Volumes

`mysql-data`, `clickhouse-data`, `vector-data` — persistent. Use `./scripts/reset-databases.sh` to wipe.

## Environment Variables

- `CONFIG_SERVICE_APPLICATION_*` — backend app config
- `VAULT_SERVICE_*` — secrets (Slack, Grafana, etc.)
- `OTEL_CLICKHOUSE_*` — OTEL collector ClickHouse connection
- `REACT_APP_*` — frontend build-time config
- `OPENFGA_*` — OpenFGA authorization service config
- `SLACK_*` — Slack OAuth integration config
- `AWS_*` — AWS credentials for Athena/S3

Credentials (defined in docker-compose, overridable via `.env`):
- MySQL: `MYSQL_USER` / `MYSQL_PASSWORD` (defaults: `pulse_user` / `pulse_password`)
- ClickHouse: `OTEL_CLICKHOUSE_USER` / `OTEL_CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD` (defaults: `pulse_user` / `pulse_password`)
- OpenFGA: `OPENFGA_STORE_ID` / `OPENFGA_MODEL_ID` (generated by init script)

## Scripts

| Script | Options |
|--------|---------|
| `build.sh` | `[--no-cache] [ui|server|cron|all]` |
| `start.sh` | `[-d|--detach] [--build]` |
| `stop.sh` | `-v` to remove volumes |
| `logs.sh` | service name (e.g., `pulse-server`, `otel-collector`) |
| `quickstart.sh` | builds + starts all |
| `reset-databases.sh` | drops volumes and reinitializes |
| `init-clickhouse.sh` | creates ClickHouse tables from schema SQL |
